{
  "texts": [
    "This approach harnesses the enhanced sentence pair modeling capabilities inherent in BERT, thereby improving the effectiveness of ABSC.",
    "This task involves classifying the sentence's sentiment towards a particular product or service category.",
    "In this example, the sentiment is positive towards the category of \"battery.\"",
    "Recent studies in COSC have explored various techniques.",
    "For instance, Liu et al. (2021) proposed a BART-based generation method that takes a more direct approach by using pre-trained language models to transform the COSC task into a natural language generation task, representing outputs with natural language sentences."
  ]
}